com.storytron.swat.verbeditor

Class OperatorMenu

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.storytron.swat.verbeditor.OperatorMenu

  • public final class OperatorMenu
extends java.lang.Object

    An OperatorMenu is a menu containing operators. It is used in script editing to insert, substitute, or replace an operator. The operators that fill the menu are queried from the OperatorDictionary.

    OperatorMenus show up in VerbEditor#mainMenuPanel.
